  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the sliced bitter melon, eggplant, and okra, and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the diced tomato and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
